data.title: Premium Festival Pass
data.meta_description: PREMIUM FESTIVAL PASS Club Skirts Dinah Shore Weekend - the largest girl party music festival in the world. Rocking Palm Springs for 30 years!
data.meta_site_name: The Dinah - the world's largest event and music festival for queer women
data.text:
DINAH PREMIUM PASSES ARE ON SALE NOW!

WITH THE PREMIUM FESTIVAL PASS, YOU CAN EXPECT:

R

ALL EVENTS & SHOWS

Entrance to all events and shows, even ones advertised after you purchase.

R

PRIORITY ADMITTANCE

Front of the line access to all events if you arrive prior to doors opening.

R

EXCLUSIVE PREMIUM LOUNGE AT THE NIGHT PARTIES

Private lounges with comfortable seating and exclusive Premium bar.

R

EXCLUSIVE PREMIUM AREA AT MARGARITAVILLE MAIN POOL

A private area at the main pool with good view of the stage.

R

PRIVATE BAR SERVICE

All PREMIUM exclusive areas have private bars exclusive to our PREMIUM Guests.

R

BOTTLE SERVICE OPTIONS

Limited amount offered exclusively to Premium Guests. VERY LIMITED QUANTITY. If you are interested, please let us know asap.

R

DINAH PREMIUM TEAM

A team of ladies to help with any and all needs at posted hours during each event.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

PREMIUM FESTIVAL PASS

R

The PREMIUM FESTIVAL PASS does NOT include hotel nights. If you want to purchase a Dinah Hotel Package, please see the DINAH HOTEL PACKAGE page.

R

Drinks and meals are not included with any ticket or package. Lawn chairs are not included.

R

Pool Towels are not provided by the hotel. You are welcome to bring your own. The Dinah will also have exclusive Dinah Commemorative Dinah towels for purchase at our Merchandise table. Towels do sell out so purchase early!.

R

All Premium Pass areas will be clearly marked.

R

All events are included in the DINAH PREMIUM FESTIVAL PASS OR DINAH HOTEL PACKAGE, even ones we announce after you purchase.
